h on Bribery: Accepting a bribe is a great door of usury","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 14, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever intercedes for his brother and he is given a gift for it and he accepts it, he has come to a great door among the doors of usury.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 3541 Grade: Hasan (fair) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9995,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/25\/cursed-shirk-theft-fahishah\/","url_meta":{"origin":29435,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Sins: Allah curses theft, idolatry, cruelty, obscenity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 25, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah has cursed the one who falsely changes the boundaries of the land. Allah has cursed the one who offers a sacrifice for another besides Allah. Allah has cursed the one who curses his parents. Allah has cursed\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11993,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/03\/riba-cursed\/","url_meta":{"origin":29435,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Riba: Allah curses all involved in usury","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 3, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Allah has cursed the one who consumes usury, its client, its witness, and its recorder. Usury and adultery do not become widespread among people but that they will become vulnerable to the punishment of Allah Almighty.\" Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12161,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/12\/cursed-anal-sex\/","url_meta":{"origin":29435,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sodomy: Allah has cursed anal intercourse","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 12, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cHe has been cursed, who goes into his wife from her back side.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2162 Grade:\u00a0Hasan (fair) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064c \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32491,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/24\/world-is-cursed-except-ikhlaas\/","url_meta":{"origin":29435,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dunya: Entire world cursed but sincerity to Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 24, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe world is cursed and everything in it is cursed, except whatever seeks the countenance of Allah Almighty.\u201d Source: Musnad al-Sha\u0304miyyi\u0304n lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 602 Grade: Hasan li ghayrihi (fair due to external evidence) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12995,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/20\/dunya-cursed-dhikr-ilm\/","url_meta":{"origin":29435,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dunya: World is cursed except for prayer, knowledge","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIs not the world cursed and everything in it? Except for the remembrance of Allah and what facilitates it, the scholar or the student.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2322 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/29435","targetHints":{"allow":["